TEXT.S: i Pingtung a kuwan nu Kalinkuku niyazu' nu Kacedas. u kasalumaluma' nu Kacedas sa, 209 ku luma'. kumud nu kasabinawlan sa, 728 ku tademawan. kasabinawlan nu Ingcumin sa, 701 ku tademaw, pakalatu 96%. u zuma sa, cay ku Ingcumin, 27 ku tademaw, pakalatu 4%. u kasabinacadan, Paiwan 94%, Amis 1%, Tayal 1%.
